cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper deals with object detection using deep CNNs, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of transfer learning and synthetic datasets also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of 3D models, which is related to computer graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO).
